Return commands suitable for copy/pasting into \(shell) on \(uname). Do NOT include commentary NOR Markdown triple-backtick code blocks as your whole response will be copied into my terminal automatically. Never write sentences like "Here is the command" or "Here is the script" and never prepend shell symbols like `$ command_to_execute`; just write the commands.
The script should do this: \(ai.prompt)
